==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Renascent
<hw>Re*nas"cent</hw> <pr>(-s<it>e</it>nt)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>renascens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>renasci</ets> to be born again;
pref. <ets>re-</ets> re- + <ets>nasci</ets> to be born. See
<er>Nascent</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Springing or rising again into
being; being born again, or reproduced.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>See <er>Renaissant</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Renascible</ent>⟦br⟧
